✅ IVAmini v1.0 Freeze Checklist
🧠 Architecture

 Clear separation between Orchestrator, Agent, Memory, LLM

 No runtime logic in __init__.py

 No circular imports

 Task creation centralized in Orchestrator

 Function signatures stable and documented

🔐 Safety & Control

 LLM has NO execution capability

 LLM cannot write memory or files

 PLAN mode cannot trigger side effects

 QUESTION mode restricted to definitions

 REVIEW mode restricted to analysis & risks

 COMMAND mode disabled or permission-gated

🧠 Memory

 Session memory is in-memory only

 Session memory clears on restart

 No disk writes during runtime

 Facts memory is read-only

 Memory injection is explicit and visible

⚙️ Runtime Stability

 System runs end-to-end from main.py

 No unhandled exceptions in normal use

 All imports resolve correctly

 Ollama connectivity errors handled gracefully

 Debug mode (if present) is optional and isolated

📦 Repo Hygiene

 .gitignore excludes venv, caches, logs

 No secrets, tokens, or absolute paths

 Repo builds cleanly on a fresh clone

 README or ARCHITECTURE.md present

🧾 Observability

 Clear task lifecycle visibility

 Optional logging (not print spam)

 [STATUS] command works

 [MEMORY] command works

🔒 Freeze Declaration

 No active refactors

 No experimental branches pending

 Baseline tag created (e.g. v1.0-local)

If all checked → IVAmini v1.0 is frozen.